  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Cubite is an extremely hard to find mineral. It's
  lightweight, strong and malleable.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>When added to other metals, even a tiny amount of Cubit=
 e can
  increase durability by 50%. Any colony with access to Cubite will r eceiv=
e a
  15% cumulative development bonus. While rare, Cubite is not a s rare as t=
he
  other super luxuries.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Occurrence: very common</span></p>
